{"tid":2253667,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳浩天涉非法集結與襲警 案件12月底裁決","createTime":"2020-10-22T10:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T11:31:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c23e75f039796a99f600c79a34a1d23d644461","tid":2253667,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"前香港民族黨召集人陳浩天被指去年「光復上水」遊行時拍打警員頭盔，就襲警及參與非法集結兩罪受審。裁判官今聽罷控辯雙方陳詞後，將案件押後至12月28日裁決。辯方今陳詞指，當日的情況猶如「同檯食飯，各自修行」，控方並無證據指被告屬於哪一個團夥。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳浩天（29歲）否認去年7月13日在上水新運路及智昌路交界與身分不詳者非法集結，以及襲擊警署警長陳國深。<br />\n<br />\n控方今邀請主審裁判官王詩麗就控方呈堂影片及相片，以及王官在庭上的觀察進行辨認比較，以確認當日的施襲者正是被告。<br />\n<br />\n辯方針對非法集結罪名指出，控方須證明被告確有參與非法集結，而呈堂片段只拍到大批人士聚集及叫囂，其中一人做出伸手動作，警署警長即指有人拍他的頭盔，這與控罪元素「三人集結並共同行動」的描述不符。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/RRCSOKXNQNDDRJCPIY544CY7XE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FRRCSOKXNQNDDRJCPIY544CY7XE%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPdAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=399a3f91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201022%2FRRCSOKXNQNDDRJCPIY544CY7XE%2F&h=b0d0d358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201022/RRCSOKXNQNDDRJCPIY544CY7XE/</a>"},{"pid":"c76d2298a96d70f7c1159da9cc43e4ed59497295","tid":2253667,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"天哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇佢香港冇今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f32f61d747473ee8c7e71411755919a5ea7dcf","tid":2253667,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c76d2298a96d70f7c1159da9cc43e4ed59497295","tid":2253667,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:22:26.000Z","msg":"天哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇佢香港冇今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686510f622655f573f694d5fa1ce11fbaca8abf5","tid":2253667,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:32:33.000Z","msg":"警甴根本亂告<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbad83465c1966e4af50dd62c72bdfb726a1ab6e","tid":2253667,"uid":55317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:33:48.000Z","msg":"王詩麗有咩事跡"},{"pid":"371e2038f72535693221c9ed719543c009a4d213","tid":2253667,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbad83465c1966e4af50dd62c72bdfb726a1ab6e","tid":2253667,"uid":55317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:33:48.000Z","msg":"王詩麗有咩事跡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:45:24.000Z","msg":"王詩麗於一九七二年在香港出生。一九九四年及一九九五年在香港大學分別取得法學士學位及法學專業證書，並於二○○四年在香港城市大學取得中國法與比較法法學碩士學位。一九九五年在香港取得大律師資格。一九九六年起私人執業，直至一九九七年加入前律政署出任檢察官，二○○○年晉升為高級政府律師。<br />\n<br />\n九龍城裁判法院主審裁判官王詩麗今天頒下判詞。指出非法集結有三項罪行元素。<br />\n裁判官指出，各被告雖不是五人在同一時刻有同一作為，但他們的作為實互有關連，非各自為政，而是共同行事。裁判官肯定五人於涉案時段於側門前集結在一起，並有着共同目的，藉各自或共同的行為令梁頌恆和游蕙禎越過保安防線進入會議室。五名被告顯然並不是為各自不同的目的而獨立行事。<br />\n【全文閱讀】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IfNR4S\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IfNR4S&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPdAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=3ffde75f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IfNR4S</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/posts/614344765575603/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fposts%2F614344765575603%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPdAsgxU2M8QNPxyQAqp636I%3D&h=a94e3d24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/posts/614344765575603/</a>"},{"pid":"0539ae9cbccdd734436c742acbb11946611b47dd","tid":2253667,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a630a9b17f2c6e82d6aba177cec0fb87ebe7cb48","tid":2253667,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:31:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}